ToxiProxy

A Perl client for ToxiProxy (https://github.com/Shopify/toxiproxy).

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc ToxiProxy

